<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Airpax - Trip Cancellation Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Client-specific resets */
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        
        /* Reset styles */
        body { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; }
        
        /* iOS blue links fix */
        a[x-apple-data-detectors] {
            color: inherit !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
        }
        
        /* Main styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #2a9d8f;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .notice-box {
            background-color: #fff3f3;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            color: #333;
            width: 35%;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 15px !important;
                border-radius: 0 !important;
            }
            .details-table th,
            .details-table td {
                display: block;
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 8px !important;
            }
            .details-table th {
                background-color: transparent;
                padding-bottom: 0 !important;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .details-table tr {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                display: block;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 22px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <!--[if mso]>
    <style type="text/css">
        body, table, td {font-family: Arial, sans-serif !important;}
    </style>
    <![endif]-->
    
    <table role="presentation" class="email-wrapper" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" width="100%">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <!--[if mso]>
                <table align="center" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="600">
                <tr>
                <td>
                <![endif]-->
                
                <div class="email-container">
                    <h2>Trip Cancellation Notification</h2>
                    <p>Dear <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
                    
                    <div class="notice-box">
                        <p>We regret to inform you that due to unforeseen circumstances, we've had to cancel your trip. Please rest assured that you will receive a full refund of your ticket amount within 5-7 working days.</p>
                    </div>

                    <h3>Trip Details:</h3>
                    <table class="details-table">
                        <tr>
                            <th>From</th>
                            <td><%= trip.from %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th>To</th>
                            <td><%= trip.to %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Journey Date</th>
                            <td><%= trip.journeystartdate %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Departure Time</th>
                            <td><%= trip.starttime %></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <h3>Refund Information:</h3>
                    <table class="details-table">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Refund Amount</th>
                            <td>Full amount paid</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Processing Time</th>
                            <td>5-7 working days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Refund Method</th>
                            <td>Original payment method</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience caused. If you need any assistance or wish to book an alternative trip, our customer support team is happy to help.</p>
                    
                    <p>
                        <strong>Contact us:</strong><br>
                        <a href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> | 
                        <a href="tel:+919990301111">+91 99903 01111</a>
                    </p>

                    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

                    <p>Best regards,<br>
                    <strong>Airpax Customer Care Team</strong></p>

                    <div class="footer">
                        <p><strong>RIGI TRANS TECH PVT LTD</strong></p>
                        <p>PERNAM INN 837/1, MANDI ESTATE, NEW DELHI - 110047</p>
                        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> | Phone: <a href="tel:+919990301111">+91 99903 01111</a></p>
                        <p><a href="https://airpax.co/">airpax.co</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!--[if mso]>
                </td>
                </tr>
                </table>
                <![endif]-->
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>